<view class="container">
  <view class="page-head watch-head">
    <text class="eyebrow">AUTHORIZED CARE</text>
    <text class="page-title">守望</text>
    <text class="page-subtitle">这里只展示本人主动授权的最小摘要。</text>
  </view>

  <view class="privacy-banner">
    <view class="banner-icon">◇</view>
    <view class="banner-copy">
      <text class="banner-title">最小授权，默认私密</text>
      <text class="banner-text">照护者无法查看原文、录音或图片，授权可由本人控制。</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view wx:if="{{loading}}" class="state-card card"><view class="state-dot"></view><text class="hint">正在加载授权摘要…</text></view>
  <view wx:if="{{denied}}" class="denied-card card">
    <view class="denied-icon">○</view>
    <view class="section-title">当前账号没有照护权限</view>
    <text class="hint">权限仅能由服务端可信配置授予，前端无法自行开启。</text>
  </view>
  <view wx:if="{{error}}" class="state-card card error">{{error}}</view>
  <view wx:if="{{!loading && !denied && !error && entries.length === 0}}" class="empty-state card">
    <view class="empty-icon">◎</view>
    <view class="section-title">暂无授权摘要</view>
    <text class="hint">本人主动分享摘要后，才会显示在这里。</text>
  </view>

  <view class="watch-card card" wx:for="{{entries}}" wx:key="id">
    <view class="row between">
      <text class="tag">{{item.type === 'text' ? '文字' : (item.type === 'image' ? '图片' : '语音')}}</text>
      <text class="hint">已授权摘要</text>
    </view>
    <text class="summary">{{item.summary}}</text>
    <view class="watch-footer"><text class="hint">{{item.createdAt}}</text><text class="source-dot">·</text><text class="hint">来自授权用户</text></view>
  </view>

  <view class="bottom-nav">
    <view class="nav-item" bindtap="goHome"><text class="nav-icon">⌂</text><text class="nav-label">首页</text></view>
    <view class="nav-item" bindtap="goMine"><text class="nav-icon">▤</text><text class="nav-label">我的</text></view>
    <view class="nav-item active"><text class="nav-icon">◎</text><text class="nav-label">守望</text></view>
  </view>
</view>
